    "paths": {
        "/generate-sale": {
            "post": {
                "summary": "Generate New Authorization",
                "operationId": "post-generate-sale",
                "responses": {
                    "200": {
                        "description": "OK",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "type": "object",
                                    "x-examples": {
                                        "Example 1": {
                                            "status_code": 0,
                                            "sale_url": "https://sandbox.payme.io/sale/generate/SALETEST-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX",
                                            "payme_sale_id": "SALE1687-957072WX-0MEX63QM-GMHDMGNU",
                                            "payme_sale_code": 1234567,
                                            "price": 1000,
                                            "transaction_id": "12345",
                                            "currency": "ILS",
                                            "sale_payment_method": "il-direct-debit"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "properties": {
                                        "status_code": {
                                            "description": "Status of the request (0 - success, 1 - error)",
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "0"
                                        },
                                        "sale_url": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "description": "The URL of the IFRAME secured payment form to display to the buyer",
                                            "example": "https://preprod.paymeservice.com/sale/generate/XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX"
                                        },
                                        "payme_sale_id": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "pattern": "XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX",
                                            "description": "Our unique sale ID"
                                        },
                                        "payme_sale_code": {
                                            "type": "integer",
                                            "description": "Our unique sale code (for display purposes only)",
                                            "example": 12345
                                        },
                                        "price": {
                                            "type": "integer",
                                            "description": "Sale final price. For example, if the price is 50.75 (max 2 decimal points) the value that needs to be sent is 5075",
                                            "example": 10000
                                        },
                                        "transaction_id": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "123456",
                                            "description": "Transaction ID"
                                        },
                                        "currency": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "ILS"
                                        },
                                        "sale_payment_method": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "il-direct-debit",
                                            "description": "The sale payment method. Must be il-direct-debit for the authorization setup process"
                                        }
                                    }
                                },
                                "examples": {
                                    "Example 1": {
                                        "value": {
                                            "status_code": 0,
                                            "sale_url": "https://sandbox.payme.io/sale/generate/SALETEST-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX-XXXXXXXX",
                                            "payme_sale_id": "SALE1687-957072WX-0MEX63QM-GMHDMGNU",
                                            "payme_sale_code": 1234567,
                                            "price": 1000,
                                            "transaction_id": "12345",
                                            "currency": "ILS",
                                            "sale_payment_method": "il-direct-debit"
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                "description": "## Overview\n\nThe Israeli Direct Debit alternative payment method works in a two-phase setup:\n1. Setting up the bank authorization <- **You are here**\n2. Completing the payment using the bank authorization\n\n### Bank Authorization Setup\n\nIn order to setup the bank Authorization, you will need to use our generate-sale endpoint, using a few specific parameters.\n1. `sale_type = token`\n2. `sale_payment_method = il-direct-debit`\n\nThe authorization page is based on our `hosted-payment-page` and will collect information regarding the buyer's identity and bank account.\n\nAfter the buyer completes the setup, the authorization will be sent to the bank and will be `inactive` until we receive an update (takes up to 96 hours).\n\n### Callbacks\n\nYou will get two callbacks:\n1. **Callback that indicates that the sale complete** - Not relevant, as the `sale_type` is from type \"token\" and not sale.<br />* You can find all the sale types [here](https://payme.stoplight.io/docs/guides/okab0oj46ivn7-sale-types)<br />* You can find all the sale callbacks [here](https://payme.stoplight.io/docs/guides/i90qmmbdut067-sale-callbacks)\n\n2. **Callback that inditates the authorization status** - You can find all the bank authorization statuses [here](https://payme.stoplight.io/docs/guides/branches/main/6biuxzskacuhb-bank-authorization-statuses).\n\n```\n{\n\"status\": 1,\n\"error_code\": \"11\",\n\"internal_reference_id\": 10000,\n\"customer_name\": \"Test test\",\n\"charge_limit\": 200\n}\n```\n\n### Testing\n\nInformation for testing can be found here - [Israeli Direct Debit Testing Information](https://payme.stoplight.io/docs/payments/branches/V1.6/v781p5enpoq9x-test-cards-and-payment-methods#israeli-direct-debit-testing-information).\n\nPlease note that in our sandbox environment you will receive only bank authorization statuses from type 1 or 2 (Success/failure). \nYou can find all the bank authorization statuses [here](https://payme.stoplight.io/docs/guides/branches/main/6biuxzskacuhb-bank-authorization-statuses).\n\n",
                "x-internal": false,
                "requestBody": {
                    "content": {
                        "application/json": {
                            "schema": {
                                "type": "object",
                                "x-examples": {
                                    "example-1": {
                                        "seller_payme_id": "MPL16370-57351SJQ-0DTLUQXA-NJ916MXU",
                                        "sale_price": "1000",
                                        "currency": "ILS",
                                        "product_name": "Shirt",
                                        "language": "en",
                                        "sale_type": "token",
                                        "sale_payment_method": "il-direct-debit",
                                        "sale_return_url": "https://sport5.co.il"
                                    }
                                },
                                "properties": {
                                    "seller_payme_id": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "The MPL the authorization will be given for",
                                        "example": "MPLDEMO-MPLDEMO-MPLDEMO-MPLDEMO"
                                    },
                                    "sale_price": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "1000",
                                        "description": "Must be included, won't be charged as a part of the authorization setup"
                                    },
                                    "currency": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "Sale currency. [3-letter ISO 4217 name](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217).",
                                        "example": "ILS"
                                    },
                                    "product_name": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "Use a generic value here (will not affect the authorization setup process)",
                                        "example": "test"
                                    },
                                    "language": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "The language the page will be presented in",
                                        "example": "he"
                                    },
                                    "sale_type": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "The sale type. For authorization setup, use `token` by default",
                                        "enum": [
                                            "token"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "sale_payment_method": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "The sale payment method. Must be `il-direct-debit` for the authorization setup process",
                                        "enum": [
                                            "il-direct-debit"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "sale_return_url": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "description": "The URL the user will be redirected to after completing the authorization setup process",
                                        "example": "https://payme.io"
                                    }
                                },
                                "required": [
                                    "seller_payme_id",
                                    "sale_price",
                                    "currency",
                                    "product_name",
                                    "sale_type",
                                    "sale_payment_method"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
